'''Manipal University''', formerly '''Manipal Academy of Higher Education''', is a [[private university|private]] research university located in the [[College town|university town]] of [[Manipal]], [[Karnataka]], [[India]]. The university has sister universities in [[Dubai]], [[Mangalore]], [[Sikkim]], and [[Jaipur]].<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.manipal.edu/AboutUs/UniversityProfile/Pages/Overview.aspx |title=Manipal University Overview  |work=manipal.edu  |accessdate=5 August 2011}}</ref> It is a member of the [[Association of Commonwealth Universities]].

